<p>This roast is exquisite!  We had some friends over we have seen in years and I&#8217;ve been wanting to try your tri tip roast for a while.  Well, last night was the night and it was a huge hit.  Everyone kept commenting about the delicious gravy.  Your recipes never let me down, Kimberly, thank you!</p>
